⁠

node.text:
Our Azrael Suit of Sorrows Gold Label 7" Figure is available for pre-order NOW exclusively at @Walmart! ⁠
Link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
This agent of the sacred Order of St. Dumas includes his sword with removable flames, a collectible art card and a base for posing.⁠
⁠
#WalmartCollectorCon #DCMultiverse

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McFarlane Toys on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Our Goofy 5" figure from Disney Mirrorverse is available for preorder NOW! Link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
Disaster seems to follow Goofy everywhere in the Mirrorverse, but he either doesn't mind or doesn’t notice! Stellar Magic has greatly amplified his luck, so it doesn't matter whether he uses a precision weapon or just tosses something over his shoulder, he always manages to hit his mark. Gawrsh!⁠
⁠
@DisneyMirrorverse #DisneyMirrorverse #Disney #ComicConAtHome #SDCC

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McFarlane Toys on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
Our Sulley 5" figure from Disney Mirrorverse is available for preorder now! Click that link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
This monstrously charismatic leader is fiercely protective -- in fact he's just plain fierce!  In the Mirrorverse, Sulley defends himself and his friends with advanced tech, slamming foes with his shield and stunning those foolish enough to get in his way.⁠
⁠
@DisneyMirrorverse #DisneyMirrorverse #Disney #ComicConAtHome #SDCC

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McFarlane Toys on July 24, 2021. May be an anime-style image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
Our Belle 5" figure from Disney Mirrorverse is available for preorder NOW! Link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
Intelligent and well-read, Belle’s love of books is matched only by her longing for adventure. In the Mirrorverse, Belle’s unconventional point of view has allowed her to discover hidden magic in her books, and cast a multitude of enchantments that heal and defend her allies when times get tough.⁠
⁠
@DisneyMirrorverse #DisneyMirrorverse #Disney #ComicConAtHome #SDCC

node.text:
Our Mickey 5" figure from Disney Mirrorverse is available for preorder NOW! Check that link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
As a boundless dreamer with eternal optimism, Mickey Mouse makes those around him feel like anything is possible. While many in the Mirrorverse seek to harness Stellar Magic, Mickey has already mastered it, calling upon its potent forces to protect those brave enough to fight alongside him.⁠
⁠
@DisneyMirrorverse #DisneyMirrorverse #Disney #ComicConAtHome #SDCC

Photo by McFarlane Toys on July 23, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text.

node.text:
Our Captain Jack Sparrow 7" figure from Disney Mirrorverse is available for preorder now! Check that link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
In the Mirrorverse, Captain Jack Sparrow’s life rises and falls with the tides – blessed with incredible luck, yet burdened by numerous curses. But Stellar Magic has allowed him to turn these things to his advantage, channeling the power of his curses to help his allies and harm his foes, all in roguish defense of the Mirrorverse.⁠
⁠
@DisneyMirrorverse #DisneyMirrorverse #Disney #ComicConAtHome #SDCC

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McFarlane Toys on July 23, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text.

node.text:
Our Buzz Lightyear 7" figure from Disney Mirrorverse is available for preorder NOW! Click the link in bio ⬆️⁠
⁠
Courageous and dutiful, Buzz Lightyear is far from your average plaything. This brave Space Ranger's super-charged suit is outfitted with an arsenal of the latest Star Command tech in the Mirrorverse, including lasers and an armor-blasting arm cannon.⁠
⁠
@DisneyMirrorverse #DisneyMirrorverse #Disney #ComicConAtHome #SDCC
